{"tid":854398,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"迷幻太空 - 吳亦凡 Kris Wu 正式發布單曲《Freedom》音樂錄影帶","createTime":"2018-10-09T10:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T13:33:54.000Z","uid":193951,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ad63b028a9f8428da91722e956372e00b1f8231b","tid":854398,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:30:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CcSGFOTX9zA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCcSGFOTX9zA&d=H8UCJd9e8g6in%2FebS35orkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=f7e387c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CcSGFOTX9zA</a><br />\n吳亦凡 Kris Wu 上月中發佈了與美國曾獲葛萊美獎三項提名的 R&amp;B 女歌手 Jhen&eacute; Aiko 合作單曲《Freedom》，如今醞釀多日，終於推出了延續以先前釋出太空迷幻形象所打造的音樂錄影帶，Kris Wu 與 Jhen&eacute; Aiko 在此音樂錄影帶中，以身處太空的環境中與不斷旋轉的畫面來帶出歌曲談論情侶對「Freedom」的定義拿捏與各式情境模擬拉扯的感覺，最終兩人不斷旋轉，並且慢慢縮小消失，為觀眾留下一個開放式結局。《Freedom》是 Kris Wu 繼與 Travis Scott 推出人氣單曲《Deserve》後的再與其他歌手合作的新歌，歌詞中呈現的情侶對於「自由」定義的拉扯與他八月初釋出的中文單曲《Hold Me Down》中的甜蜜情感相當不同，也似是在模擬情侶戀愛中所遭遇的過程。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zkcWfZE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzkcWfZE.gif&h=b9bf3cba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c21b00e5f489dd21bf67fd90d89bd0e4d562138f","tid":854398,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:38:32.000Z","msg":"太牛B了<br />\n666666666666666666"},{"pid":"117e723365970590e1da07230f1d58426b99fdcb","tid":854398,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"太skr<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3vMDgP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3vMDgP.gif&h=25a36579&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1f1ce375940426557b63525392eae26264ad32c","tid":854398,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"666666666666666666666666"},{"pid":"5400970c7692d1a6fc8a0d97ff5302bc22fdb287","tid":854398,"uid":52073,"like":